            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Gherardus">Gherardus</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Bonitius">Boniti</name></persName> offre
                        pro anima sua, del defunto padre e della defunta madre al <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/126">San Bartolomeo</orgName> sito loco
                            <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/281">Sestinghe</placeName>,
                        due <rs key="#Petiae">appezzamenti</rs> di terra: il primo, una <rs
                            key="#Wine">vigna</rs> posto in loco <placeName key="#Petiae #Wine"
                            ref="#places/274">Morrano</placeName> prope Strata, confinante ambas
                        capitas con terra della <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">chiesa</rs> di
                            <orgName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/125">San Donato</orgName>, lato uno con terra di
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Consortes/shared_possessions"><name
                                ref="Farulfus">Farolfo</name></persName> et de suis <rs
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortibus</rs>, alio lato con
                        terra e <rs key="#Wine">vigna</rs> del suddetto <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Wine" ref="#juridical_persons/126"
                            >monastero</orgName> di <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Wine"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/126">S. Bartolomeo</orgName>; il secondo, un <rs
                            key="#Acorns">quercieto</rs> posto ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Acorns">Pissinalita</placeName>, tenentes uno
                        capo in terra <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Acorns"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti Bartholomei</orgName>, alio capo
                        tenet in terra <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/124">Sancti Laurentii</orgName> qui fuit quondam
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Rainerius"
                                >Raneri</name></persName>, lato uno tenet in terra qui fuit quondam
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gherardi</name></persName>, et alio lato tenet in terra <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Consortes/shared_possessions"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rodilandi</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Rainerius">Raneri</name></persName> et de suis
                            <rs key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortibus</rs>, con tutte le
                        loro dipendenze. Chiede a <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini imperatoris la stesura della cartula.
                        Actum in loco et finibus ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Castle"
                            ref="#places/282">Valli</placeName>, prope ipso <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castello</rs>. Testimoni: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Azo"
                                >Actii</name></persName> filio bone memorie item <persName><name
                                ref="Azo">Actii</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandi</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Fraolmus">Fraolmi</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Albitius">Albitii</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Sigitius">Sighitii</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Ildus">Ildi</name></persName>. Scrive: Rodulfus
                        notarius domini imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
